# Eventora — Design System Specification

Panduan visual lengkap untuk seluruh komponen dan halaman Eventora.

---

## 1. Color Palette

### Primary Colors
| Token | Hex | RGB | Usage |
|-------|-----|-----|-------|
| `--primary` | `#059669` | 5,150,105 | Tombol utama, link, CTA, icon aktif |
| `--primary-dark` | `#047857` | 4,120,87 | Hover tombol, navbar aktif |
| `--primary-light` | `#D1FAE5` | 209,250,229 | Badge background, highlight row |
| `--primary-50` | `#ECFDF5` | 236,253,245 | Section background alternatif |

### Accent Colors
| Token | Hex | Usage |
|-------|-----|-------|
| `--accent-rose` | `#F43F5E` | Badge "Popular", harga diskon, notifikasi |
| `--accent-amber` | `#F59E0B` | Bintang rating, warning |
| `--accent-blue` | `#3B82F6` | Link info, badge "Baru" |

### Neutral Colors
| Token | Hex | Usage |
|-------|-----|-------|
| `--bg` | `#FAFAF8` | Background utama halaman |
| `--surface` | `#FFFFFF` | Card, modal, dropdown |
| `--foreground` | `#1E293B` | Teks utama (heading, body) |
| `--muted` | `#64748B` | Teks sekunder, placeholder |
| `--border` | `#E2E8F0` | Border card, divider, input |
| `--border-hover` | `#CBD5E1` | Border hover state |

### Gradient Presets
```css
--gradient-hero: linear-gradient(135deg, #ECFDF5 0%, #FAFAF8 50%, #FFF1F2 100%);
--gradient-cta: linear-gradient(135deg, #059669 0%, #047857 100%);
--gradient-footer: linear-gradient(180deg, #064E3B 0%, #022C22 100%);
--gradient-card-shine: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.2) 0%, transparent 50%);
```

---

## 2. Typography

### Font Stack
| Role | Font Family | Fallback | CSS Variable |
|------|------------|----------|-------------|
| Display/Heading | Playfair Display | Georgia, serif | `--font-serif` |
| Body/UI | Inter | system-ui, sans-serif | `--font-sans` |

### Type Scale
| Element | Size Desktop | Size Mobile | Weight | Line Height | Font |
|---------|-------------|-------------|--------|-------------|------|
| H1 Hero | 72px (4.5rem) | 40px (2.5rem) | 700 | 1.1 | Serif |
| H2 Section Title | 40px (2.5rem) | 28px (1.75rem) | 700 | 1.2 | Serif |
| H3 Card Title | 24px (1.5rem) | 20px (1.25rem) | 600 | 1.3 | Sans |
| H4 Subsection | 20px (1.25rem) | 18px (1.125rem) | 600 | 1.4 | Sans |
| Body Large | 18px (1.125rem) | 16px (1rem) | 400 | 1.7 | Sans |
| Body | 16px (1rem) | 15px | 400 | 1.6 | Sans |
| Small/Caption | 14px (0.875rem) | 13px | 400 | 1.5 | Sans |
| Badge/Label | 12px (0.75rem) | 12px | 600 | 1.4 | Sans |

### Text Colors
- Heading: `--foreground` (#1E293B)
- Body: `--foreground` (#1E293B) at 90% opacity
- Muted: `--muted` (#64748B)
- Link: `--primary` (#059669)
- On Primary BG: `#FFFFFF`

---

## 3. Spacing & Layout

### Spacing Scale (rem)
```
4px  = 0.25rem  → gap antar icon kecil
8px  = 0.5rem   → padding badge, gap antar item kecil
12px = 0.75rem  → padding tombol kecil
16px = 1rem     → padding card, gap grid
24px = 1.5rem   → margin antar elemen
32px = 2rem     → section padding horizontal
48px = 3rem     → gap section mobile
64px = 4rem     → gap antar section
96px = 6rem     → section padding vertical desktop
```

### Container
- Max width: `1280px` (80rem)
- Padding horizontal: `16px` mobile, `24px` tablet, `32px` desktop

### Grid
- Template gallery: `3 kolom` desktop, `2 kolom` tablet, `1 kolom` mobile
- Feature grid: `3 kolom` desktop, `2 kolom` tablet, `1 kolom` mobile
- Pricing cards: `3 kolom` (scroll horizontal mobile)

### Breakpoints
| Name | Min Width | Tailwind |
|------|-----------|----------|
| Mobile | 0px | default |
| Tablet | 768px | `md:` |
| Desktop | 1024px | `lg:` |
| Wide | 1280px | `xl:` |

---

## 4. Components

### Buttons

**Primary Button**
```
Background: --gradient-cta
Text: white, 16px, font-weight 600
Padding: 12px 32px
Border-radius: 9999px (full rounded)
Shadow: 0 4px 14px rgba(5,150,105,0.3)
Hover: scale(1.02), shadow lebih besar
Active: scale(0.98)
Transition: all 200ms ease
```

**Outline Button**
```
Background: transparent
Border: 1.5px solid --primary
Text: --primary, 16px, font-weight 600
Padding: 12px 32px
Border-radius: 9999px
Hover: bg --primary-50, border --primary-dark
```

**Ghost Button**
```
Background: transparent
Text: --muted, 16px, font-weight 500
Padding: 8px 16px
Hover: bg --primary-50, text --primary
```

### Cards

**Template Card**
```
Background: white
Border: 1px solid --border
Border-radius: 16px
Shadow: 0 1px 3px rgba(0,0,0,0.04)
Hover: shadow 0 8px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.08), translateY(-4px)
Transition: all 300ms ease
Overflow: hidden (untuk thumbnail)

Structure:
┌─────────────────────┐
│  [Thumbnail 16:10]  │
│  aspect-ratio       │
├─────────────────────┤
│  Category Badge     │
│  Template Name      │
│  Price              │
│  [Preview] [Pakai]  │
└─────────────────────┘
```

**Pricing Card**
```
Default: bg white, border --border, radius 24px, padding 32px
Popular: border 2px --primary, shadow 0 8px 30px rgba(5,150,105,0.15)
Popular Badge: bg --accent-rose, text white, -8px top offset
Header: gradient --gradient-cta untuk plan popular
```

**Feature Card**
```
Background: --bg atau white alternating
Border: 1px solid --border
Border-radius: 16px
Padding: 24px
Icon container: 48x48px, bg --primary-light, radius 12px
```

### Inputs
```
Height: 48px
Background: white
Border: 1px solid --border
Border-radius: 12px
Padding: 0 16px
Font: 16px, --font-sans
Focus: border --primary, ring 3px --primary-light
Placeholder: --muted
```

### Badges
```
Padding: 4px 12px
Border-radius: 9999px
Font: 12px, weight 600, uppercase, letter-spacing 0.05em

Variants:
- Default: bg --primary-light, text --primary-dark
- Popular: bg --accent-rose, text white
- New: bg --accent-blue, text white
- Free: bg --primary-50, text --primary
```

### Navbar
```
Position: fixed, top 0, z-50
Background: rgba(250,250,248,0.8)
Backdrop-filter: blur(12px)
Border-bottom: 1px solid --border
Height: 64px
Logo: Playfair Display, 24px, bold, --primary
```

---

## 5. Animations (Framer Motion)

### Page Load
```tsx
// Hero text fade-in dari bawah
initial={{ opacity: 0, y: 30 }}
animate={{ opacity: 1, y: 0 }}
transition={{ duration: 0.8, ease: "easeOut" }}
```

### Scroll Reveal (semua section)
```tsx
initial={{ opacity: 0, y: 40 }}
whileInView={{ opacity: 1, y: 0 }}
viewport={{ once: true, margin: "-100px" }}
transition={{ duration: 0.6, delay: index * 0.1 }}
```

### Card Hover
```tsx
whileHover={{ y: -4, scale: 1.01 }}
transition={{ type: "spring", stiffness: 300, damping: 20 }}
```

### Stats Counter
```tsx
// Animate dari 0 ke target number
// Duration: 2 detik
// Easing: easeOut
// Trigger: whileInView
```

### FAQ Accordion
```tsx
// AnimatePresence untuk expand/collapse
initial={{ height: 0, opacity: 0 }}
animate={{ height: "auto", opacity: 1 }}
exit={{ height: 0, opacity: 0 }}
transition={{ duration: 0.3, ease: "easeInOut" }}
```

### Floating Elements (Hero)
```tsx
// Parallax cards
animate={{ y: [0, -15, 0] }}
transition={{ duration: 4, repeat: Infinity, ease: "easeInOut" }}
```

---

## 6. Landing Page Section Specs

### 6.1 Hero
- Background: `--gradient-hero` mesh gradient
- Floating decorative blobs: emerald & rose, blur 80px, opacity 0.1
- Center aligned text content
- Event type pills below heading (horizontal scroll mobile)
- Below CTA: mockup frame showing invitation preview

### 6.2 Template Showcase
- Background: `--bg`
- Section title + subtitle centered
- 4-column grid desktop, 2 mobile
- Show 8 templates, "Lihat Semua" button below
- Each card has thumbnail, name, price, category badge

### 6.3 Stats Counter
- Background: `--gradient-cta` (emerald gradient)
- 4 stats in a row, white text
- Numbers animate counting up on scroll
- Icons above each stat
- Full-width banner style

### 6.4 Features
- Background: white
- 3-column grid with icon, title, description
- 14 feature cards total
- Alternating section bg possible

### 6.5 How It Works
- Background: `--primary-50`
- 3 steps horizontal with connecting line
- Each step: number circle, icon, title, description
- Step circles connected by dashed line

### 6.6 Pricing
- Background: `--bg`
- 6 cards, horizontal scroll on mobile
- "Pro" card highlighted with emerald border + "Popular" badge
- Toggle: Per Undangan / Berlangganan
- Expandable feature rows with check/cross icons

### 6.7 Testimonials
- Background: white
- Auto-scrolling horizontal carousel
- Each card: quote text, customer name, event type, star rating
- Dots indicator below

### 6.8 FAQ
- Background: `--bg`
- Accordion list, max-width 768px centered
- Click to expand answer, chevron rotates
- Smooth height animation

### 6.9 Footer
- Background: `--gradient-footer` (dark emerald)
- 4 columns: Brand + desc, Navigasi, Bantuan, Kontak
- White/light text
- Payment method icons row
- Bottom bar: copyright + version

---

## 7. Invitation Theme Design Specs

### Shared Structure (semua tema)
```
┌─────────────────────────────┐
│  COVER (fullscreen)         │
│  - Opening animation        │
│  - "Buka Undangan" button   │
├─────────────────────────────┤
│  COUPLE SECTION             │
│  - Photo(s), names, parents │
├─────────────────────────────┤
│  EVENT DETAILS              │
│  - Akad & Resepsi           │
│  - Date, time, venue        │
│  - Save to Calendar btn     │
├─────────────────────────────┤
│  COUNTDOWN                  │
│  - Days / Hours / Min / Sec │
├─────────────────────────────┤
│  LOVE STORY (optional)      │
│  - Timeline with dates      │
├─────────────────────────────┤
│  GALLERY                    │
│  - Photo grid / carousel    │
├─────────────────────────────┤
│  RSVP FORM                  │
│  - Name, attendance, wishes │
├─────────────────────────────┤
│  GUEST WISHES (live feed)   │
├─────────────────────────────┤
│  GIFT REGISTRY              │
│  - Bank account(s)          │
│  - Copy button              │
├─────────────────────────────┤
│  GOOGLE MAPS EMBED          │
├─────────────────────────────┤
│  FOOTER                     │
│  - "Powered by Eventora"    │
│  - Background music toggle  │
└─────────────────────────────┘
```

